	<td width="98%">
	
		<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
		<tr>

		
			<tr>
				<td><font face="verdana" size="1">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="/quests/default.asp">Quests</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="default.asp?land=121218">West Cabilis</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline3.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<b>Flaxen Hilt, Sorcer's Skullcap</b><br><br>
				</td>
			</tr>
				
			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Flaxen Hilt, Sorcer's Skullcap</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=157864"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:">JustAGuy9999999</a> | 
		                        6/20/2000 2:06:20 PM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">The Hermit is located near the exit to the Lake of Ill Omen. This post is to 'break out' this quest from the general Necro skullcap quest thread as only speculation regarding this is there, and it's burried.<BR>
You say, 'hail an iksar hermit'<BR>
an iksar hermit   looks at you with one good eye.  His left eye is covered with puss.  I seek a [great sorcerer]. <BR>
You say, 'i am a great sorcerer'<BR>
[It&#8217;s based on BroodOfKotiz Faction, with Faction improved by killing Iksar outcasts...]<BR>
Your faction standing with BroodOfKotiz got worse.<BR>
an iksar hermit   hands you a flaxen hilt or handle of sorts.  It has four round slots on one end.  Insert within what used to be.  Return it to me when all is complete.  With it shall be your Sorcerer's Skullcap.  Go and prove your knowledge.<BR>
[A Flaxen Hilt: LORE, weight 1.0, usable by all. Not a &#8216;combine&#8217; quest container]
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><font face="verdana" size="2">
				<a href="/UserUpdate.asp?id=157864">
				[Add Comments] Add info on this quest!</a><br><hr>
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><font face="verdana" size="2">

